{"tid":2426812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟要求港府立即釋放被捕民主派人士","createTime":"2021-02-28T10:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T15:43:27.000Z","uid":21470,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"a944d75fbc0649a6698c7e94949765131698d2a3","tid":2426812,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:48:08.000Z","msg":"歐盟要求港府立即釋放被捕民主派人士<br />\n<br />\n55名組織及參去年參與民主派初選的人士到警署報到，其中47人被警方以「串謀顛覆國家政權罪」落案起訴，他們會被通宵扣留。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟駐港澳辦事處在社交網站發聲明指關注事件，要求立即釋放被捕人士，又指事件清楚反映香港不再容許合法的政治多元化，促請港府及北京遵守《基本法》和《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》對自由和法治的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2380965\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2380965&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3q7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=e54f9087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2380965</a>"},{"pid":"5f5459e27477a71cddfec42d918549f9f72046bf","tid":2426812,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:48:53.000Z","msg":"得幾百人retweet緊，你地幾時肯做嘢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊做任 好冇?<br />\n<br />\n國際媒體<br />\nPost World<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/postworld/status/1365914080138178560\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpostworld%2Fstatus%2F1365914080138178560&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3q7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=ad2da022\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpostworld%2Fstatus%2F1365914080138178560&h=e3513d52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/postworld/status/1365914080138178560</a><br />\n<br />\nReuters<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Reuters/status/1365892036122062848\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FReuters%2Fstatus%2F1365892036122062848&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3q7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=3bbe5649\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com